function getAndroidArch() {
    switch (config_1.Config.osArch()) {
        case 'arm':
            return 'armeabi-v7a';
        case 'arm64':
            return 'arm64-v8a';
        case 'x86':
        case 'x32':
        case 'ia32':
        case 'ppc':
            return 'x86';
        case 'x86-64':
        case 'x64':
        case 'ia64':
        case 'ppc64':
            return 'x86_64';
        default:
            return config_1.Config.osArch();
    }
}
